ATTRIBUTION NOTE (non-binding, but intended):

This repository references the publicly-published investment and macroeconomic
frameworks of Ray Dalio, available at:
  - https://www.economicprinciples.org
  - https://www.bridgewater.com/research-and-insights
  - Ray Dalio's LinkedIn long-form posts

Where non-Dalio sources are used to close gaps, they are explicitly marked
"NON-DALIO (industry standard)" with full citations and public URLs.

No copyrighted text beyond minimal fair-use snippets is embedded in this
repository. All frameworks are described in this repository's authors' own
words with proper attribution.
